    "row": 15,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "# 为什么？"
  },
  {
    "row": 16,
    "rowsha": "dPuYXMG7AWCCGoq3Tp1LY698NvZ4LD6f8HK8TSNN0GA=",
    "originContent": "# Why?",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 17,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "你可以用 *[ratatui](https://ratatui.rs/)* “烹饪”一个终端。但你能**油炸**一个终端吗？"
  },
  {
    "row": 18,
    "rowsha": "yhLBExcsRwix4GJBJ9WPbLf9LJML/JW4r/sJtgaqAqk=",
    "originContent": "You can *[cook](https://ratatui.rs/)* a terminal. But can you **deep fry** a terminal?",
    "translatedContent": "*能！* 你可以**烹饪*并且*油炸**你的 `tty`！~~趁还没迟赶紧跑！~~"
  },
  {
    "row": 19,
    "rowsha": "bQVWesJ/+dHxfz/g0f9oq9rokl18oXvw5jhw6Mc1pu8=",
    "originContent": "*YES!* You can **cook *and* fry** your `tty`! ~~Run before it's too late!~~",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 20,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "> 终端通常处于“烹饪”模式，或称规范模式。"
  },
  {
    "row": 21,
    "rowsha": "MwkPX9odL3XKWrt6ToZ8CmFB1XjxwCxlt9tpHjT1bAE=",
    "originContent": "> The terminal is usually in \"cooked\" mode, or canonical mode.",
    "translatedContent": "> 使用 `ratatui`🐁，它处于原始模式，但它会为你“烹饪”。"
  },
  {
    "row": 22,
    "rowsha": "zxWa117Y7ugf+Sn5GN0r4nSd2/9PSKYheaiIxYTUkw4=",
    "originContent": "> With `ratatui`🐁, it's in raw mode, but it \"cooks\" for you.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 23,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "Markdown 显然可以在终端中很好地渲染，但有一个关键方面缺失："
  },
  {
    "row": 24,
    "rowsha": "X1LB8VwpH/40hMKtvoPh8g381g0XYYF2Oi3NW3jAD/k=",
    "originContent": "Markdown can obviously be rendered pretty well in terminals, but one key aspect is missing: ",
    "translatedContent": "大标题™ 让文本更易读，且内联渲染图片非常方便。"
  },
  {
    "row": 25,
    "rowsha": "eJeDn3XSE/6QOA1eBFpj7tRBYt3admnj+NooLcL67ho=",
    "originContent": "Big Headers™ make text more readable, and rendering images inline is very convenient.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 26,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "# 怎么做？"
  },
  {
    "row": 27,
    "rowsha": "Ldy4IZ0hjDIq93mBPg/qGYRnytzJrIwpApkkJiaZhpY=",
    "originContent": "# How?",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 28,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "通过将标题作为 [ratatui 图片](https://github.com/benjajaja/ratatui-image)渲染，"
  },
  {
    "row": 29,
    "rowsha": "QbeYBJJlHCWNzn7JwJ05fXkboz+a9vIMVb0izULCMK8=",
    "originContent": "By rendering the headers as [images with ratatui](https://github.com/benjajaja/ratatui-image),",
    "translatedContent": "并使用几种终端图形协议之一：Sixels、Kitty 或 iTerm2。"
  },
  {
    "row": 30,
    "rowsha": "6D60xRxkHtmOuZPfGKZxd/WENeBEWgFVcDfWlEVW3Is=",
    "originContent": "and using one of several terminal graphics protocols: Sixels, Kitty, or iTerm2.",
    "translatedContent": "Kitty 终端还实现了一个 [文本缩放协议](https://sw.kovidgoyal.net/kitty/text-sizing-protocol/)"
  },
  {
    "row": 31,
    "rowsha": "MZjUhQXVfxpCW8VSNlYisgIBy7uCCay+qsIDCZMbpko=",
    "originContent": "The Kitty terminal also implements a [Text Sizing Protocol](https://sw.kovidgoyal.net/kitty/text-sizing-protocol/)",
    "translatedContent": "可以直接缩放文本，无需渲染成图片！"
  },
  {
    "row": 32,
    "rowsha": "AqDay38ub+8mokjTiNIsEULRfKSaDhvDpCtnhJQpgrc=",
    "originContent": "to directly scale text without needing to render as images!",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 33,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "请参见 [ratatui-image](https://github.com/benjajaja/ratatui-image?tab=readme-ov-file#compatibility-matrix)"
  },
  {
    "row": 34,
    "rowsha": "DIZhEaYgE7cJVs5rCAr6SqpLB+sy3hs22q62ePFd1Oc=",
    "originContent": "See [ratatui-image](https://github.com/benjajaja/ratatui-image?tab=readme-ov-file#compatibility-matrix)",
    "translatedContent": "查看你的终端是否支持图形，以及更多细节。"
  },
  {
    "row": 35,
    "rowsha": "0a9MOYQa+naZlOHVgLvvf6FkXFp1ZZBtTSI40lAVhMg=",
    "originContent": "to see if your terminal does even have graphics support, and for further details.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 36,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "一般来说，Kitty、WezTerm、iTerm2、Ghostty、Foot、`xterm -ti vt340`，*应该*都能用。"
  },
  {
    "row": 37,
    "rowsha": "nE9iuTUqtkl4+euhkpIXFUDwN/L41oJ5KRP2zR05CvU=",
    "originContent": "In general, Kitty, WezTerm, iTerm2, Ghostty, Foot, `xterm -ti vt340`, *should* work.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 38,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "在完全不支持图形的终端，如 Alacritty，图片则使用 Chafa 渲染。"
  },
  {
    "row": 39,
    "rowsha": "Ab6gBVXMh74Xo6XiUOVbDH8rzFvGoxPrhqy8EP9K3Q0=",
    "originContent": "On terminals without graphics whatsoever, like Alactritty, images are rendered with Chafa.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 40,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 41,
    "rowsha": "oEvHgiQZPffZY71LXkD7wBebC/0+TjyYxWZNyVCJCpU=",
    "originContent": "# Installation",
    "translatedContent": "# 安装"
  },
  {
    "row": 42,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 43,
    "rowsha": "wsEIpB3ceMevym7EqpAB5B3skavSNde201NJVZrM69Q=",
    "originContent": "* Rust cargo: `cargo install mdfried`",
    "translatedContent": "* Rust cargo: `cargo install mdfried`"
  },
  {
    "row": 44,
    "rowsha": "yaxegIlCdxi9Ygz2vm6PbplpRIa+BRmx9ku6wZV4sOo=",
    "originContent": "  * From source : `cargo install --path .`",
    "translatedContent": "  * 从源码安装：`cargo install --path .`"
  },
  {
    "row": 45,
    "rowsha": "m26kBsXolGSaqqbFw5imktlXPCiBv4zHWEAtMmCn+4Y=",
    "originContent": "  * Needs a chafa package with development headers, usually called something like `libchafa-dev`, `libchafa-devel`, or just `libchafa`, or even just `chafa`.",
    "translatedContent": "  * 需要带有开发头文件的 chafa 包，通常名称类似 `libchafa-dev`、`libchafa-devel`、或者只是 `libchafa`，甚至直接叫 `chafa`。"
  },
  {
    "row": 46,
    "rowsha": "//7V0cS5rGWJ3JenA1WtCaADQFe5qAuP09TuCJe8VI0=",
    "originContent": "  * If chafa is not available at all, or you don't care about it because your terminal supports some graphic protocol, then use `--no-default-features`.",
    "translatedContent": "  * 如果完全没有 chafa，或者你不在意它，因为你的终端支持某些图形协议，可以使用 `--no-default-features`。"
  },
  {
    "row": 47,
    "rowsha": "rO1skARMh3+cXsBabEqJiF+K3M/UZIbA7Jk0rtpN0eo=",
    "originContent": "  * If `cargo install ...` fails, try it with `--locked`, and/or report an issue.",
    "translatedContent": "  * 如果 `cargo install ...` 失败，尝试加上 `--locked`，或者报告一个问题。"
  },
  {
    "row": 48,
    "rowsha": "hH+ZfM2doY6vlofWM6ldSXIpJb4oEBL+aoKqNaqw7N4=",
    "originContent": "* Nix flake: `github:benjajaja/mdfried`",
    "translatedContent": "* Nix flake: `github:benjajaja/mdfried`"
  },
