  {
    "row": 59,
    "rowsha": "8bkBhHOQsO1+N058HkZOwXtGpCfEh6WtbL0pBkBQg9U=",
    "originContent": "```",
    "translatedContent": "```"
  },
  {
    "row": 60,
    "rowsha": "eLQFV9ddee/BQZWSqfjJ+hbVQHaD5EP9oP1dOJOQ9H0=",
    "originContent": "mdfried ./path/to.md",
    "translatedContent": "mdfried ./path/to.md"
  },
  {
    "row": 61,
    "rowsha": "8bkBhHOQsO1+N058HkZOwXtGpCfEh6WtbL0pBkBQg9U=",
    "originContent": "```",
    "translatedContent": "```"
  },
  {
    "row": 62,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "除非您使用的是 Kitty 0.40 版或更高版本，或终端不支持任何图形协议，"
  },
  {
    "row": 63,
    "rowsha": "SJzOphjZ2lWlhXAjpeKn3v8so3rW7aDaOVk4HqQN9wg=",
    "originContent": "Unless you're using Kitty version 0.40 or greater, or a terminal that does not support any graphics",
    "translatedContent": "否则第一次运行 `mdfried` 时，您需要选择一个字体。"
  },
  {
    "row": 64,
    "rowsha": "eVoATLWKpZIOGz9GfCjbWrgKlkG9DoEyE4rmEf9jpnE=",
    "originContent": "protocol, the first time you run `mdfried` you will have to pick a font.",
    "translatedContent": "您应该选择与终端正在使用的字体相同的字体，但也可以选择任何字体。"
  },
  {
    "row": 65,
    "rowsha": "Y+vVylQnxgdceUZGGNMs3iAb0eHhEWJO7mznQnB/3q4=",
    "originContent": "You should pick the same font that your terminal is using, but you could pick any.",
    "translatedContent": "字体设置屏幕允许您搜索系统字体——您需要选择与终端正在使用的字体相同的字体。"
  },
  {
    "row": 66,
    "rowsha": "wfQYNcMlmmlKU/S9yy6SvFp2y3XY4VjTAWVBbU/s1jM=",
    "originContent": "The font-setup screen lets you search the system fonts - you will want to pick the same font that",
    "translatedContent": "字体将直接以预览形式呈现。"
  },
  {
    "row": 67,
    "rowsha": "pEaoyXQo8WQjX4toHPryceWPNAG9LaFeLsGX61RrW4I=",
    "originContent": "your terminal is using.",
    "translatedContent": "确认后，选择将写入配置文件。"
  },
  {
    "row": 68,
    "rowsha": "ukWNAFbP590gdvV8ZDOMhyfzS7jwgNFGbsqUkWlRpoA=",
    "originContent": "The font is rendered directly as a preview.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 69,
    "rowsha": "qAaHKRUupKvxVkXU0L+E7oe795PFd7tc4bEjnQoXWWk=",
    "originContent": "Once confirmed, the choice is written into the configuration file.",
    "translatedContent": "如果字体不正确，可以使用 `--setup` 强制重新设置字体。"
  },
  {
    "row": 70,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 71,
    "rowsha": "oJWP1VEDRJMywBORpw8PXLKt/uKBIKepGb2+emRD/Rk=",
    "originContent": "Use `--setup` to force the font-setup again if the font is not right.",
    "translatedContent": "您也可以将 Markdown 内容通过管道传入："
  },
  {
    "row": 72,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
